
vagrant up
vagrant ssh head01
bash /vagrant/smrtanalysis_2.3.0.140550_libc-2.5_centos-53.run --rootdir /smrtanalysis
(and follow the instruction, mostly pressing enters, use localhost as the hostname)
(after installed, use /smrtanalysis/admin/smrtportal-initd start to start)
(use host safari/firefox to log on http://localhost:8080)
(register administrator)
(then start to use your mini cluster)
